 &HT;    Makeup, li'l Mindy
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   AUSTIN, Texas _
</P>
<P>
   Makeup Mindy ($20; www.eToys. com) Hasbro has developed one heck
of a cool product that will have your little girl playing out her
own salon scene. Don't worry, this makeup is mess-free; after
chilling Mindy's beauty accessories (beauty mask and makeup
applicator) in the freezer for a couple of hours you can use them
to apply eye shadow, blush, nail polish and lipstick. Mindy also
comes with a hair dryer that blows cold air and changes her hair
color from her natural shade to bright pink and purple. Recommended
age, three and up. The blow dryer requires two AA batteries.
</P>
