<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Hapless heroes are back
 &HT;    By Staff Reports
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _
</P>
<P>
   Rocky the Flying Squirrel and Bullwinkle J. Moose, TV cartoon
heroes from your parents' childhoods, are returning _ this time
appearing on the big screen _ to stop baddies Boris and Natasha.
Can the squirrel and the moose save the world? ``The Adventures of
Rocky and Bullwinkle'' hits theaters Friday.
</P>
<P>
   WHO'S KNOCKING?
</P>
<P>
   Eight-year-old Michael Martin has a knock-knock joke to share.
Knock-knock. Who's there? Needle. Needle who? I needle little hug.
Thanks, Michael! And remember, everyone: Send your jokes to NFK, 72
Marietta St., Atlanta, Ga. 30303, and we'll print the best ones we
get!
