<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-26 14:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5188 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e BC-MOVIE-STORM-BOS &LR;      06-26 1657
