international premium passengers now is available to the general
public. The QuietComfort Acoustic Noise Cancelling headset from
Bose is designed to block or compensate for background noise so the
audio that reaches the listener's ears will be identical to what he
would hear in a quiet room. (Cummings, Dayton Daily News). MOVED.
