   10 MONTHS, 10 MINUTES, $10 MILLION
</P>
<P>
   BC-ECOM-VENTURE-CAPITALISTS _ The partners in a start-up called
WebTaggers.com recently spent an anxious day and a half preparing
to present their business plan to venture capitalists at a
conference in Austin, Texas. Within a mere 10 minutes, they were
required to secure the money to become an overnight Internet
success, complete with an initial public offering and a listing on
Nasdaq. This story recounts their high-stress day. By Courtney
Barry.
</P>
