<P>
   INTERNATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO-ELECTION _ MEXICO CITY _ An advance story that will
profile Mexico as a country _ contradictions, poverty levels,
educational snapshot, its standing in the world as a major economy
or Third World wannabe _ and sum up what has emerged as core issues
of the campaign. We would talk to voters and whether they see the
election as pivotal, what they hope for and why. Developing.
(Ferriss, Cox News Service). WITH PHOTOS and map-graphic produced
by the Austin American-Statesman with several elements.
</P>
