Cambridge, (800) 233-1234, $320 on weekends and $264 weekdays;
Fifteen Beacon, $595, (877) 982-3226; Charles Hotel, starting at
$295, (800) 888-1818; Sheraton Boston Hotel, $225, (800) 325- 3535;
and the Wyndham Boston, $375 Monday through Thursday and $259
Friday through Sunday, (800) 822-4200.
</P>
<P>
   The following are offered on weekends only: Fairmont Copley
Plaza, starts at $249, (800) 866-5577; Hyatt Harborside, $225,
(800) 233-1234; Le Meridien, $299, (800) 791-7781; Royal Sonesta
