   MANAGED CARE COMPANIES ARE SUED  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Six managed care companies were accused of misleading health
plan members in lawsuits filed in a federal district court in
Miami, where a judge recently promised a speedy decision in a
similar suit against Humana.  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   WEBVAN IS BUYING HOMEGROCER.COM  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   The much-anticipated consolidation of the online grocery market
got under way with the announcement that the Webvan Group would
acquire HomeGrocer.com in a stock swap valued at approximately $1.2
billion.
</P>
